citation.case_name: Bourne, a Minor, by and Through His Parents, Next Friends and Natural Guardians, Bourne v. E.I. Du Pont De Nemours & Co

html:
543 U.S. 917

BOURNE, A MINOR, BY AND THROUGH HIS PARENTS, NEXT FRIENDS AND NATURAL GUARDIANS, BOURNE ET AL.
v.
E.I. DU PONT DE NEMOURS & CO.
